        Returns Flowable emitting FluxRecords which are matched the query. If none found than return Flowable.empty().
        Parameters:
        query - the Flux query to execute
        orgID - specifies the source organization
        Returns:

      • query

        <M> io.reactivex.Flowable<M> query(@Nonnull
                                   String query,
                                   @Nonnull
                                   String orgID,
                                   @Nonnull
                                   Class<M> measurementType)
        Execute a Flux against the Flux service.
        Type Parameters:
        M - the type of the measurement (POJO)
        Parameters:
        query - the flux query to execute
        orgID - specifies the source organization
        measurementType - the class type used to which will be result mapped
        Returns:
        Flowable emitting a POJO mapped to measurementType which are matched the query or Flowable.empty() if none found.
